Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and VNW Independent are pleased to present for sale Salitage Estate, an award winning and renowned Western Australian winery and vineyard.

Located in the heart of Pemberton, one of Australia's most well-recognised premium wine regions, Salitage Estate is a highly respected brand and an icon of the Australian wine industry. An extensively developed 51.75Ha* landholding across three Certificates of Title, the key features of Salitage Estate can be described as follows:

- A highly productive 22.83Ha* vineyard, planted predominantly to Pinot Noir, Cabernet Sauvignon, Chardonnay and Sauvignon Blanc, with some minor plantings of Petit Verdot, Cabernet Franc and Merlot.

- Custom-built, modern winery complex spanning three levels and featuring a winery with crushing capacity for 450 tonnes, a substantial barrel store, administration office, gallery and entertainment area and a cellar door with ample on-site parking.

- High quality structural improvements, including the three bedroom main homestead, four bedroom manager's residence and the Salitage Suites, four two bedroom self-contained chalets providing guest accommodation and tourism opportunities.

- Further improvements include a workshop, storage shed, pump shed and a chemical store.

- Highly productive, free draining soil types, as well as gently undulating topography rising from the Vasse Highway.

- Excellent irrigation infrastructure, underpinned by outstanding water supply provided by three storage dams with a total capacity of approximately 138 megalitres.

- Pemberton is recognised globally for the production of award winning cool climate wines, and Salitage Estate, comprising the Salitage and Treehouse labels, is a showpiece of the region, having been established in 1989.

- Numerous awards, including the coveted Austrade sponsored award as Exporter of the year (2008/09), Gourmet Traveller Wine's best cellar door in 2013 and 2014, and the Ray Jordan accolade in his annual wine guide as Best in the West in consecutive years.

- An incredibly scenic and highly visited tourist destination, surrounded by Karri forests, waterfalls, rivers and lakes and boasting numerous attractions, including street artscape, art galleries, restaurants and cafes and boutique accommodation.

- Outstanding 'Walk In Walk Out' opportunity

For Sale by Expression of Interest closing 4pm Wednesday 23 September 2015.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE in conjunction with Caravan Park Brokers Australia are pleased to present for sale the Albany Gardens Holiday Resort and Lifestyle Village. 

The sale of Albany Gardens Holiday Resort and Albany Gardens Lifestyle Village presents an opportunity to acquire a significant landholding, a well established holiday resort business and a fully occupied lifestyle village, in the heart of Albany, the largest City in the Southwest of Western Australia. 

Key Investment Highlights: 

- Resort - 119 sites incl. 16 cabins, 31 ensuite caravan sites, 36 powered caravan sites, 18 camp sites and 18 park homes
- Village - 45 permanent sites (100% occupied)
- Recreational facilities incl. Pool, tennis court, camp kitchen and games rooms
- Central to the commercial district on a 5.65Ha* site (4.034Ha* resort / 1.616Ha* village)
- Albany is a drive in drive out destination, with outstanding natural beauty and attractions

Albany Gardens Holiday Resort and Albany Gardens Lifestyle Village are being offered For Sale as a Going Concern in-one-line for $5,500,000 firm.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Hotels are delighted to present to the market the freehold ‘walk in walk out’ opportunity of the Midas Motel, Kalgoorlie.  

The Midas Motel, located at 409 Hannan Street, is configured across three buildings (two single levels and a double level building) developed over a 5,063sqm* landholding and is perfectly positioned on the main arterial link between Perth and Kalgoorlie. 

The Motel comprises 48 rooms varying in size from single, double and family accommodation, separate managers residence, reception, restaurant, function area plus swimming pool surrounded by manicured gardens and BBQ facilities.

This well-established motel is generating consistent weekly revenue and is ideally suited to a hands-on operator. Leveraging off a booming resource sector and strong corporate activity, including regional hospital and other Government services, Kalgoorlie, with its increasing tourist appeal is primed for strong business returns for many years to come. 

The Motel is for sale via an Expressions of Interest.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Hotels is pleased to present to the market Seasons Hotel Newman – a continually strong performing regional accommodation asset offering a significant footprint, in land and rooms, in the resource-rich, north-west of Western Australia. 

Positioned at the entrance of the Newman town centre, this 89 room asset presents an opportunity to purchase a highly profitable long-term accommodation business, with substantial growth and expansion potential, as the WA resources sector goes from strength to strength. 

Investment Highlights: 

- An established hotel comprising 89 accommodation rooms, a la carte dining, bar, swimming pool and conference facilities
- A 2019 annual occupancy of 51% with an average room rate of $175 per night
- 31% of FY19 annual revenue was achieved in the last quarter – highlighting the impact of the ramping up of resources projects in the area 
- Limited competing accommodation assets in Newman
- Significant landholding of 2.90Ha* with potential to add room count if desired

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE in conjunction with Active West Real Estate is pleased to present to market the opportunity to purchase this substantial Geraldton CBD Foreshore development site, located on Marine Terrace.

The most strategically located development site of scale in Geraldton, this truly generational opportunity offers a range of commercial and residential uses with potential for 5 levels and expansive ocean views.

- Suitable for retail, hotel, residential, commercial, large format, medical, aged care & others
- 3 extensive street frontages on Marine Terrace, Lester Avenue and Fitzgerald Street across 4 Super Lots
- 100m* to the waters edge and direct access to the foreshore parklands and recreation area
- Includes the Geraldton Beach Hotel, Bottlemart, Marine Terrace tenancies and Lester Avenue showrooms / warehouse.
- Residual holding income across numerous tenancies with opportunity for improvement and extension
	
The property benefits from favourable planning controls and has a ‘Regional Centre’ zoning that allows for a 5-storey development with bonuses available should performance criteria be met.  

The properties are available in-one-line, as individual lots or any combination of lots.

For more information please contact the exclusive selling agents.
